revision.text: ==Venetian== ===Etymology=== From {{inh|vec|la|iuvenem|iuvenem, juvenem}}, accusative of {{m|la|iuvenis}}, from {{inh|vec|itc-pro|*juwenis}}, from {{der|vec|ine-pro|*h₂yuh₁en-}}. Compare {{cog|it|giovane}}. ===Adjective=== {{vec-adj|xovan|e|i}} # [[young]], [[youthful]] ===Noun=== {{vec-noun|xovan|m|e|i}} # young man # [[youth]]
